channel.title: Bruce Lee
channel.description:
This isn't really a review, but one of my biggest inspirations in life is Bruce Lee, and I just happened to come across a video that shows several different pictures of him throughout his life time, many that are somewhat rare. I think this kind of stuff is cool, so if you do too, here is the video.
[youtube]https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VqKs9FdiihQ[/youtube]
If this isn't in the right section, I'm very sorry!
